dialogue: Haha, that was a close one! The slimes got you, huh?
Don't worry, they're bouncier than they look. Happens to the best of us!
Maybe try aiming for the squishier ones next time. Or was that your plan all along?
You can always give it another shot. I promise I won't laugh... much.
Remember, pressing down in mid-air helps you land faster and bounce higher!
Come on, I know you can do it!
